data.description: $10,000 seller credit with full price offerThis home on over half an acre has it all! Five bedroom, 3.5 baths, with a formal dining room, office, and media/movie room. No detail has been overlooked; rustic wood flooring, granite countertops throughout. The kitchen boasts an island, stainless steel appliances, and overlooks the family room with wood burning fireplace. 2 of the 5 bedrooms as well as media/movie room and full bath located upstairs. The backyard oasis with brick patio, outdoor fireplace, separate fire pit, and a 12x16 Garden House that offers both beauty and functionality. Located in the desirable Brownstone Manor neighborhoodCall to schedule your showing today!
